<title type="html"><![CDATA[5/7 topic : man's best friends]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=726&amp;p=754#p754"><![CDATA[
5/7 topic : man's best friends<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1i-QYIx-7QnNFdqFfbnIQyW4Cp20Hw0Ir/edit?usp=sharing&amp;ouid=115535931921506206490&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1i-Q ... ue&amp;sd=true</a><!-- m --><br />man's best friends<br /><br />1.Do you have any experience about keeping a pet? <br />2.Have you ever heard about any novel and thoughtful service for pets?<br />3.What kind of animal will be your favorite and why?<br />4.Do you agree that keeping pets is good for your physical and mental health? Reason?<br /><br />Agenda：<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XPpUKQsKS7_rKF2HfGhtIVPcevh9rDet/edit?usp=sharing&amp;ouid=115535931921506206490&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XPp ... ue&amp;sd=true</a><!-- m --><br /><br />breakthroughs in business<br />1.Could you briefly compare the possible career path of an Asian in different countries or regions such as US, Europe or China? <br />2.On the other hand, do you think it’s easy or not for a foreigner to get promoted in Taiwan?<br />3.If possible, will you let your kids go abroad for study? Why or why not?<br />4.According to the article, do you think &quot;bamboo ceiling&quot; really exist to Asian workers? Is it from outside or inside? Do you have any good idea to breakthrough or remove it?<br /><br />Agenda：<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Mon May 01, 2023 8:25 pm</p><hr />
